FBIS4-34352 "drlat118_b_94007" FBIS-LAT-94-118 Daily Report 17 Jun 1994 Haiti Anti-Drug Brigade Destroys 268 Kilos of Cocaine Anti-Drug Brigade Destroys 268 Kilos of Cocaine FL1706222994 Port-au-Prince Radio Metropole in French 1600 GMT 17 Jun 94 FL1706222994 Port-au-Prince Radio Metropole French BFN [Excerpt] On 16 June in the presence of journalists, the Haitian anti-drug service destroyed 268 kilos of cocaine from Colombia, intended for the U.S. market. The cocaine, seized during recent months by the Haitian anti-drug brigade, was thrown in the sea offshore by a unit of the Haitian Navy, aboard which were journalists and photographers who were invited to cover the event. [passage omitted]
